panels.description:
Duration of one call to poll `TransactionsManager` future, and its nested function calls.

Network Events - stream peer session updates from `NetworkManager`;
Transaction Events - stream txns gossip from `NetworkManager`;
Pending Transactions - stream hashes of txns successfully inserted into pending set in `TransactionPool`;
Pending Pool Imports - flush txns to pool from `TransactionsManager`;
Fetch Events - stream fetch txn events (success case wraps a tx) from `TransactionFetcher`;
Fetch Pending Hashes - search for hashes announced by an idle peer in cache for hashes pending fetch;
(Transactions Commands - stream commands from testnet to fetch/serve/propagate txns)

Durations of one call to poll `NetworkManager` future, and its nested function calls.

Network Handle Message - stream network handle messages from `TransactionsManager`;
Swarm Events - stream transaction gossip from `Swarm`
